RecFwk 0.3 API

Packages
com.isnotworking.recfwk.engine Provides implementations for the main framework interfaces.
com.isnotworking.recfwk.filters Provides interfaces and implementations for data filters.
com.isnotworking.recfwk.io Provides implementations for data input and output.
com.isnotworking.recfwk.model Provides basic entities for implementing and conducting experiments with recommenders: Items, Recommendations, Users etc.
com.isnotworking.recfwk.util Provides misc utils: I/O, statistics and probability, performance measuring, string manipulation etc.
com.isnotworking.recfwk.vis Provides interfaces and implementations for representing performance results and experiment parameters graphically.
